'''Mya Nalle''' was one<ref name="Insider" /> of the [[Nalle triplets]], a trio of [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|females]] offered by [[Mayor/Legends|Mayor]] [[Acros-Krik]] as guides to targets he wanted monitored. She reported to the mayor any useful information their guests foolishly divulged.<ref name="Databank">{{DB|character|acros_krik|Acros-Krik}}</ref>

She was at the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] shortly before the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|outbreak]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].<ref name="AOTC">{{Film|II}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Mya Nalle was portrayed by [[Amy Allen]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].<ref name="Insider" /> The name is an anagram of "Amy Allen."

